---
const raw = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const base = raw.endsWith('/') ? raw : raw + '/';
---

<section class="landing-section cta-section text-center">
  <h2>Recovery is worth protecting.</h2>
  <p class="lead" style="margin-inline:auto;">
    Multi-layer blocking. Real tamper resistance. Accountability built in. Privacy respected. Open source and free.
  </p>
  <div class="cta-group" style="margin-top:2rem;">
    <a href={`${base}getting-started/`} class="btn-primary">Get Started Free</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/JerrettDavis/BetBlocker" class="btn-secondary">View on GitHub</a>
  </div>
</section>
